animeTitle: Pokemon Fushigi no Dungeon: Shutsudou Pokemon Kyuujotai Ganbaruzu!
otherNames: Pokemon Mystery Dungeon: Team Go-Getters Out of the Gate!, Pocket Monsters Advanced Generation - S3 Pokemon Mystery Dungeon: Team Go-Getters Out of the Gate!, ポケモン不思議のダンジョン 出動ポケモン救助隊ガンバルズ！
synopsis: A human wakes up one day to discover that he has become a Squirtle in a world filled with natural disasters, where he meets Charmander and Chikorita of Team Go-Getters, a Pokemon rescue team. Squirtle joins Team Go-Getters for the task of saving Pichu's Brother Pikachu from Skarmory, however Gengar and his Team Meanies decide to interfere.
